name: MarathonPacingCalculator
0:
”Alexa, ask marathon pacing calculator pace for 4 hour marathon”
”Alexa, ask marathon pacing calculator what is the pace for 3 hour and 30 minutes marathon?”
”Alexa, ask marathon pacing calculator 2 hour marathon pace.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: marathon pacing calculator
des: Ever wonder how fast you need to run for a certain marathon goal? This skill tells you exact that, in both minutes/mile and minutes/km.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
